{"tid":803645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙灣天主教墳場逾80個骨灰龕墓碑遭破壞","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T06:53:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef193272072ef2c50360fba963c6c6cd3d0af7b0","tid":803645,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1415826_1_L_20180902190714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1415826_1_L_20180902190714.jpg&h=abfc3c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣天主教墳場有80多個龕位墓碑遭破壞，警方列作刑事毀壞案處理，便衣探員到場調查，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據墳場保安人員表示，遭破壞的龕位墓碑屬於48至54段，即接近墳場山頂的位置。現場所見，受破壞的龕位墓碑，大部分屬夫妻合葬，先人遺照及碑文損毀，周圍佈滿碎片；部分墓碑亦被擊穿，可以清楚看見內裡的骨灰盅。<br />\n<br />\n有孝子賢孫表示，先人的龕位墓碑已嚴重損毀，批評犯案者沒有良心，亦不滿墳場保安措施不足，估計犯案者以為墓碑內有貴重物品而作案。亦有市民表示，父母安葬於涉事地段，擔心墓碑損毀，所以到場了解，查看後發現龕位墓碑無恙。"},{"pid":"41543de3cb034d06e4e014fe626d9081b756cb19","tid":803645,"uid":48973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;估計犯案者以為墓碑內有貴重物品而作案。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n轉才"},{"pid":"306d48ce4ef1dd228bd389bf593b0d5d00678543","tid":803645,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"大陸人做？"},{"pid":"397d5fb79adf4fea3d447ed0e423aa32753421aa","tid":803645,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"306d48ce4ef1dd228bd389bf593b0d5d00678543","tid":803645,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"大陸人做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"似係"},{"pid":"6121e478b6dfe340a01c8579d534d412ab22c988","tid":803645,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"無祈禱？"},{"pid":"b2f2f8635a84f423feeaf09dddf7888eca62c93f","tid":803645,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1415923_1_L_20180903123353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1415923_1_L_20180903123353.jpg&h=ec8b4eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣天主教墳場有超過80個骨灰龕墓碑昨日被發現受破壞，繼續有家屬到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n有墳場辦事處職員早上為受破壞龕位拍照作記錄，又提醒家屬不要觸碰受破壞的墓碑，以免影響警方套取指紋。<br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區副主教陳志明說，昨晚已即時加強保安，稍後會作檢討。"},{"pid":"b46ef1cac4331aed42f854d991319078b2e94f7b","tid":803645,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"摸金校尉？"},{"pid":"5097a3ce8ecbc404f23c094f51ed57b899772443","tid":803645,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"Tomb Raider"}]}